Title: Camelot
Plot: SG-1 discovers the village of Camelot on an alien world, and must face Merlin's security system when they go in search of an Ancient weapon. Elsewhere, Earth and its allies assemble a fleet when a working Ori Supergate is discovered.
GuestStars: Claudia Black, John Noble, Katharine Isabelle, Matthew Glave, David Thomson, Eric Steinberg, Gary Chalk, Martin Christopher, Peter DeLuise
